eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu was there. #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Inland schools reopened, but there are some serious problems. Frustrations over the Gauteng school online application process are boiling over in the West Rand. Angry parents are threatening to shut down the District offices if their children aren't placed in schools by tomorrow. Scores of parents queued for a third day at the offices. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has the details in the video above.